title: David Benham arrested outside North Carolina abortion clinic: 'It's government overreach'
description: Conservative activist David Benham was arrested Saturday for sidewalk counseling outside a North Carolina abortion clinic despite a stay-at-home order amid the coronavirus pandemic.
